edu.cpp.cs.cs141.vetadmin

Class Registry

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cpp.cs.cs141.vetadmin.Registry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Registry
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents the registry for the vet clinic. It contains all of the Pet Records and Owners registered in the system. All Pets and Owners are registered and deregistered through the registry.
    See Also:
